    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_184.png[/img]{The man nods.%SPEECH_ON%Fair enough. I know that when I came across my intellectual superior, I grew jealous and refused any help he provided. Well, good sir, may you travel well and catch up to me and my discoveries!%SPEECH_OFF%}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_184.png[/img]{The man nods.%SPEECH_ON%Fair enough. I know that when I came across my intellectual superior, I grew jealous and refused any help he provided. Well, good sir, may you travel well and catch up to me and my discoveries!%SPEECH_OFF%}\""
